race.comment: MISS ENVY (7) has a strong record here with eight wins and eight placings from 19 starts. Hit the frame latest (29.90) when third at this track in a OPEN. Expected to go close. TILLY ROSE (3) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a 0.8 lengths third (42.45) behind WEST ON ACE at this track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can measure up. ICONIC JET (6) goes very well at the course with four wins and a placing from nine starts. Recorded a 1.5 lengths win (29.70) in a Free For All last time at this track. Looks well placed here and among the chances. LINGUINE MONELLI (1) was out of placings last time (30.16) at this track in a OPEN, finishing fourth and beaten 6 lengths. Has already won three times from this draw.
